<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Currently only INNER JOIN and LEFT JOIN is supported in Zend_Db_Select.</p>

<p>Add methods {{joinRight()}}, {{joinFull()}}, {{joinCross()}}, and {{joinNatural()}}.</p>

<p>For methods {{joinCross()}} and {{joinNatural()}}, no {{$cond}} parameter is needed (though the SQL standard permits a condition for these joins too).</p>

<p>It is not required to support natural joins other than inner joins.</p>

